== QUICKLAUNCH-BOX (FAVOURITES-SELECTOR) ==
[done] Implement quicklaunch-box
[done] Clicking quicklaunch icon starts application and quits
- Allow drag-n-drop of quicklaunch icon to windows-list view and start app in current workspace and quit
- Allow drag-n-drop of quicklaunch icon to workspace-box, start app in this workspace and quit

== WORKSPACE-BOX (WORKSPACE-SELECTOR) ==
- Implement workspace-box
- Clicking on workspace-actor switches to workspace and quits
- Mouse-wheel on workspace-actor switches workspace without quitting but updating windows-list view

== VIEWPAD (VIEW AGGREGATOR) ==
[done] - Implement viewpad
[done] - For each view create a button to switch to this view
[done] - Check why we need to slowly double-click on text to switch view - should be single-click
[done] - Scroll bars should be shown or hidden automatically depending on if view fits the space in this direction

== WINDOWS-LIST VIEW ==
[done] Implement windows-list view
[done] Click live-window actor
- Multi-monitor support (show visible windows on the screen where it belongs to, fullscreen over all screens)
- Allow closing window by clicking "X" button of live-window actor
- Allow drag-n-drop of live-window actor to quicklaunch-box view and create shortcut
- Allow drag-n-drop of live-window actor to another workspace by dropping window in workspace-box
- React on new window appearing by creating a live-window actor for it
- React on window disappearing by destroying appropiate live-window actor

